page.title: 17FOOD CONT.
page.content: Spaghetti originally came from Italy. It can be in long pieces or in pieces about 3_4 cm long.Invaders are pieces of spaghetti, shaped like space_craft. Haunted House is spaghetti pieces in the form of bats, ghosts and other scary things. Noodle Doodles are different shapes of spaghetti like hearts, houses, cars and other shapes. Spaghetti Rings are pieces of spaghetti shaped as rings.Baked Beans are a type of white bean with a tomato sauce.All of these foods have tomato sauce with them. Sandwiches are quite popular they are made from 2 pieces of bread and butter wih a type of filling in between, such as jam, peanut butter or cheese. Sweets and crisps are also very popular with children.Chocolate comes in a bar also you can get chocolate coated things with fillings.
